{
  "stem": "14060.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But on the other hand, this was a big plus for me, because I had no difficulty with that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we started off in the [INAUDIBLE] lager, the tent camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then eventually, somehow, we managed to [? will ?] ourselves into the main camp, where amongst all the blocks-- and there were some of them two stories high-- there was only one Jewish block, block 22.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were Jews and important prisoners of-- politically important prisoners of Jews who were taken to Buchenwald already years and years before from, from, from France, from Germany, and so on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that summer of 1944, they made another block-- block number 23, a Jewish block.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I must say, life there was-- considering it was a concentration camp-- quite tolerable.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't the worst.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father and my brother had to go out to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a [INAUDIBLE], which was a, a stone quarry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What they did there didn't build the German Reich.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "However, that was their occupation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I, a being a relatively young guy, [? wheedled ?] my way around in, in the block.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I used to do messages and carrying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I did not go out daily to do the hard work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And maybe that also helped me that I didn't get so quickly weakened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The-- because There was also a, a little wood workshop in, in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And sometime, I went in to work there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, I was sort of sent in between places, and I maneuver.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But before we were taken-- before we got into that block 23, I remember in [INAUDIBLE], there was a Russian prisoner of war who was deaf mute-- deaf and dumb.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I sat on the ground, you know, during the day.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
